"Oh yeah." Rumble agreed, the fresh air felt good as it glided along his
body. Just being able to move after so many years of confinement. "First
we find this wannabe con, then we find Megatron, then we get back at
that stupid Tripredicus Council." Rumble grumbled, listing off his
priorities.
